<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>One Line Can Change a Life</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

<button id="theme-toggle" aria-pressed="false">🌙 Dark Mode</button>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="particles">
        <span>{ }</span>
        <span>&lt;/&gt;</span>
        <span>HTML</span>
        <span>CSS</span>
        <span>JS</span>
        <span>&lt;code&gt;</span>
    </div>

    <div class="code-box">
        <code id="code"></code>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h1 id="title">One Line Can Change a Life</h1>

        <p class="intro">
            Every app we use...
            Every message we send...
            Every online payment we make...
            Every opportunity we discover...
            began with a single line of code.
        </p>

        <button onclick="showMessage()">
            Discover More
        </button>

    </div>

</section>

<section class="story">

    <h2>One Line Can Change a Life</h2>

    <p>
        Thousands of people use technology every day without thinking about
        the code behind it.

        A simple line of code can connect families, educate children,
        help doctors save lives, empower businesses,
        or inspire someone to chase their dreams.

        Today, I write my first line of code.

        Tomorrow, it could become someone's first opportunity.
    </p>

    <div class="quote">
        "Every great innovation started with one line of code.
        Today, I write mine."
    </div>

</section>

<section class="footer">
    <p>Built with ❤️ using HTML, CSS & JavaScript</p>
</section>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
